title: Which signs mean what?(like gtg or np)
body:
Hey guys
I would like to ask what the signs like np or gtg... mean.Can anybody give me a list so i know what these signs mean?It would be great because my brother always laugh at me because i dont know what the signs mean.XD

replies.body: I see what you did there

It is something you pick up over time, but here are some common ones. Btw they are called acronyms.

Afk= away from keyboard
Lol= laugh out loud
LoL= league of legends
Rofl= rolling on the floor laughing
Cs= creep score (how many minions you have killed)
Kda= kill death assist ratio
Jitb= jack in the box
GA= guardian angel
RoA= rod of ages
LW= last whisper
Adc= attack damage carry

Ok imma stop myself XD
If you have any more specific ones then fire away.

Star signs?

NP GTG = NOOB PHUCK GET TILTED GOOBER
gtg is 'got to go'. np is 'no problem'.
